  <summary date="2017-12-20T05:00:00Z" status="Introduced in House">Inclusive Campuses Act

This bill amends the Higher Education Act of 1965 to allow historically black colleges and universities and other minority-serving institutions of higher education to use federal aid provided under title III of the Act to establish resource centers on campus that provide support to and education about lesbian, gay, bisexual, transgender, and queer students.</summary>
